OL,3,CAlex Salmond says he made a 'mistake'
OL,4,Cimmediately after independence
OL,5,Creferendum
OL,7,FAlex Salmond has told ITV Border he
OL,8,Fmade a 'mistake' in standing down as
OL,9,FFirst Minister immediately after
OL,10,Flosing the 2014 independence
OL,11,Freferendum.
OL,13,FMr Salmond says he now feels leaving
OL,14,FBute House was 'a daft thing to do',
OL,15,Fclaiming 'manifest opportunities' to
OL,16,Fadvance the independence cause had
OL,17,Fbeen missed.
