OL,3,CAlex Salmond says he made a 'mistake'
OL,4,Cimmediately after independence
OL,5,Creferendum
OL,7,FHis claims brought a sharp response
OL,8,Ffrom his successor as First Minister,
OL,9,FNicola Sturgeon, who told us: "nobody
OL,10,Fhas a greater conceit of Alex Salmond
OL,11,Fthan Alex Salmond."
OL,13,FThe two former First Ministers, who
OL,14,Fwere once close but whose relationship
OL,15,Fhas broken down, were speaking as part
OL,16,Fof a Representing Border special
OL,17,Fprogramme for ITV Border, A Decade of
OL,18,FDebate.
