OL,3,CAlex Salmond says he made a 'mistake'
OL,4,Cimmediately after independence
OL,5,Creferendum
OL,7,FMr Salmond, who left the SNP and now
OL,8,Fleads the Alba Party, said: "I thought
OL,9,Fto make a point of departure for the
OL,10,Freferendum in the future was a right
OL,11,Fthing for the national movement.
OL,12,FLooking back, that was a mistake.
OL,14,F"Now, in retrospect, that was a daft
OL,15,Fthing to do. But then... I thought we
OL,16,Fwere set for independence in a
OL,17,Freasonable timescale."
OL,26,@pD@]OUvD@AOU
