OL,3,CAlex Salmond says he made a 'mistake'
OL,4,Cimmediately after independence
OL,5,Creferendum
OL,7,FHe added: "If you'd told me then that
OL,8,Ften years later, we'd still be waiting
OL,9,Fdespite the manifest opportunities
OL,10,Fthere have been, then I would have
OL,11,Fsaid, 'Well, I'll just hang about then
OL,12,Fand see the matter through."
OL,14,FAsked about his comments, Ms Sturgeon
OL,15,Fwho was Mr Salmond's political protege
OL,16,Fand chosen successor, said: "I think
OL,17,Fwhat anybody, supporter or opponent of
OL,18,FAlex, will say is nobody has a greater
OL,19,Fconceit of Alex Salmond than Alex
OL,20,FSalmond.
