OL,7,F"So clearly he's going to think that
OL,8,Fhe could have done things so much
OL,9,Fbetter. I say that in as gentle a way
OL,10,Fas possible, to coin one of his
OL,11,Ffavourite phrases."
OL,13,FThe now backbench MSP said she was no
OL,14,Flonger 'best friends' with Mr Salmond
OL,15,Fbut at the time she wanted him to stay
OL,16,Fon as leader.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@SO]
