OL,3,CAlex Salmond says he made a 'mistake'
OL,4,Cimmediately after independence
OL,5,Creferendum
OL,7,F"When he said to me in the early hours
OL,8,Fof the morning after the referendum
OL,9,Fthat he intended to resign, I tried to
OL,10,Ftalk him out of it. It became clear
OL,11,Fthat wasn't going to work.
OL,13,F"I think he miscalculated. I think he
OL,14,Fthought the SNP was going to go into a
OL,15,Fdownward spiral after the referendum
OL,16,Fand he possibly didn't want to hang
OL,17,Faround for that."
OL,19,FMs Sturgeon said she had taken time to
OL,20,Fconsider if she wanted to take on the
OL,21,Fleadership role.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUyD@QO]
