OL,3,CAlex Salmond says he made a 'mistake'
OL,4,Cimmediately after independence
OL,5,Creferendum
OL,7,F"It was more a sense of I don't want
OL,8,Fjust to sort of almost by default say,
OL,9,F'yes I'm going to put myself forward.'
OL,10,FI wanted to take a moment to ask
OL,11,Fmyself some hard questions.
OL,13,F"Not just 'did I really want it' but
OL,14,F'did I actually really think I was
OL,15,Fcapable of it?'. It was a sense of
OL,16,Fneeding take a step back and reflect,
OL,17,Fwhich I did, and we know what happened
OL,18,Fafter that."
